<AbstractNarration>Abstract  CTS-0217595 &lt;br/&gt;                                                                                                                                                                                  Funds are requested for the purchase of a stereoscopic particle imaging (SPIV) system for flow measurements.  Proposed projects will include flow in a stirred tank reactor, resuspension of bottom sediments, flows in micro-channels, and stratified flows.  These projects will be carried out by four members of faculty in Civil and Environmental Engineering, Mechanical Engineering and Architecture Engineering Departments.&lt;br/&gt;</AbstractNarration>
